 Our findings also have policy implications: public and private actors in
 the agriculture sector need to promote new technologies as highly site-
 and context-specific combinations of technologies, inputs, practices, and
 efforts instead of single 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

miracle seeds
\begin_inset Quotes erd
