 to inform their subsequent adoption decisions.
 The effect of incorrect expectations about future returns on decision-making
 has been studied most in the context of investments in education, but is
 readily applicable to technology adoption in agriculture.
 For example, both 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "nguyen2008information"
