 improved variety 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(Y_{it}^{H}\right)$
\end_inset

 and inputs used 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(X_{it}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A first group of farmers knows that, for the adoption premium to materialize,
