\begin_layout Standard
Finally, we investigate how the intervention affects the use of inputs (other
 than seed) and practices.
 Recall that for inputs and practices, the effect is expected to be positive,
 but only weakly so (see Prediction 4 in Section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:Theoretical-framework"
