\end_inset

 At least some treated farmers who had dis-adopted in response to new informatio
n and more realistic expectations are, in fact, cultivating the new variety
 again; these may now be in for the long run.
 This indicates that the video did not increase dis-adoption per se; it
 only accelerated dis-adoption that was going to happen at some point.
\end_layout

